 engagement with Australian landscapes. In J. Anderson (ed.), Cambridge companion to Australian art, pp.&nbsp;11–21. Cambridge University Press, Melbourne. # 2012. '''Taçon, P.S.C.''', June Ross, Alistair Paterson, and Sally May. Picturing change and changing pictures: Contact period rock art in Australia. In J. McDonald and P. Veth, eds., A Companion to rock art. Oxford: Wiley-Blackwell, 2012. {{ISBN|978-1-4443-3424-1}}
